title: Raise all-source coverage gates to 100/100/100/100
description: "Replace the earlier 90/80/90/90 regression floor with legitimate complete coverage of every src TypeScript file, including CLI bootstrap and package exports, without ignore directives, artificial branches, duplicate tests, or coverage exclusions."
