severity: critical
environment: "Current baseline 95.44 statements, 84.75 branches, 96.30 functions, 96.11 lines with src/cli.ts and src/index.ts excluded"
repro_steps: "Run bun run test:coverage and inspect the all-files summary plus vitest.config.ts exclusions"
resolution: "Included CLI bootstrap and exports in V8 coverage, added focused unit/integration/command tests, removed unreachable branches, and raised all four thresholds to exactly 100."
expected_result: Every src TypeScript file is measured and all four coverage metrics are exactly 100 without exclusions or ignore directives.
actual_result: "Vitest passes 1,186 tests in 110 files at 100% statements, 100% branches, 100% functions, and 100% lines."
